{"tid":1122374,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱同個fd坐小巴，佢同我講洗乜戴安全帶呀on9。。。","createTime":"2019-04-24T02:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T03:00:15.000Z","uid":216662,"like":2537,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"c6bb35e2f54aa2f7ad9617eb1b301189690d153f","tid":1122374,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T02:15:29.000Z","msg":"是咁的～<br />\n<br />\n啱啱同朋友坐小巴，見幾滿人我地就坐最後雙人位，我一坐低就好慣性咁戴安全帶，之後個朋友就大大聲話我<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> on9咁大個人仲戴安全帶  </span></span>，全車人都聽到攪到周圍啲人都望下我笑。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話口未完滿座司機開車，一開車突然坐最前面有一男一女叫司機停車，原來係便衣放蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿sir抄完前面頭先笑到好開心但無戴安全帶嗰幾條友就抄我朋友，佢俾人抄嗰陣我忍笑忍到幾乎瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後阿sir同我朋友講：下次要學你朋友上車戴安全帶啦，知到無？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最最後我喺車笑到瀨哂屎，俾人抄嗰幾條友好似想打鳩我咁嘅樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點算好？"},{"pid":"2f1543c1774517798de89c391241c4855b6e5e99","tid":1122374,"uid":55851,"like":1273,"dislike":10,"score":1263,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T02:17:21.000Z","msg":"記住抺返乾淨啲屎先好走"},{"pid":"b88412b8adc66d5afdea3db27867b130664e8a4f","tid":1122374,"uid":470,"like":739,"dislike":6,"score":733,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T02:20:06.000Z","msg":"雖然樓主FF<br />\n但我都有frd試過坐小巴無戴安全帶比人罰錢"},{"pid":"8b07f90ed1e19e2f6c2f5a0c2019b4cb63306959","tid":1122374,"uid":216662,"like":122,"dislike":7,"score":115,"quote":{"pid":"2f1543c1774517798de89c391241c4855b6e5e99","tid":1122374,"uid":55851,"like":1273,"dislike":10,"score":1263,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T02:17:21.000Z","ms